Use `backcap bridges` to see which bridges exist in your project:

```bash
npx @backcap/cli bridges
```

The CLI reads `bridge.json` manifests from your local `bridges/` directory and displays:

```
Bridges

  auth-audit-log
    Source: auth | Target: audit-log
